## Selected biography

*   [**Prabowo Subianto Djojohadikusumo**](/Prabowo_Subianto)
    Official portrait, 2024

    [Prabowo Subianto Djojohadikusumo](/Prabowo_Subianto) (born 17 October 1951) is an Indonesian politician, businessman, and former military officer who has served as the eighth [president of Indonesia](/President_of_Indonesia) since 2024. He previously held the position of the 26th [minister of defense](/List_of_Ministers_of_Defense_(Indonesia)) under President [Joko Widodo](/Joko_Widodo) from 2019 to 2024. Prabowo is notable as Indonesia's third president with a military background, following in the footsteps of [Suharto](/Suharto) and [Susilo Bambang Yudhoyono](/Susilo_Bambang_Yudhoyono). He also holds the distinction of being the oldest individual to begin their first term as president in Indonesian history.

    Prabowo graduated from the [Indonesian Military Academy](/Indonesian_Military_Academy) (Akademi Militer Nasional) in 1970. His military career was primarily spent within the Special Forces ([Kopassus](/Kopassus)), culminating in his appointment to lead the Strategic Reserves Command ([Kostrad](/Kostrad)) in 1998. Later that same year, he was discharged from the military and subsequently faced a ban from entering the [United States](/United_States) due to alleged human rights abuses. ( [Full article...](/Prabowo_Subianto) )

