## Did you know

*   A little trivia to keep you vaguely entertained.

*   ... that the [Javanese](/Javanese_people) eat [cat rice](/Nasi_kucing) (pictured)? Don't ask me why. It's their business.

*   ... that a [Muslim "pope"](/HB_Jassin) in Indonesia translated the [Quran](/Quran) after being tried for blasphemy? An interesting twist of fate, wouldn't you say?

*   ... that [Ismail Saleh](/Ismail_Saleh) served the longest tenure as [Minister of Justice of Indonesia](/List_of_ministers_of_law_and_human_rights_of_Indonesia)? Longevity is often overrated.

